  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/140",
  "title": "Add the major version number to the url",
  "body": "This will add the instantsearch major version number to the url, under the `is_v` name (for `i`nstant`s`earch `v`ersion).\n\nWe currently do nothing with it yet, but this is for future reconciliation between old url and new instant search version.\n\nThe diff about `onPopState` is simply refactoring of moving the function in its own method.\n",
